reviewText:
This movie is a great movie. My son loves it! One of his favorite movies, hes almost 3.
We came across it on accident but so glad we did. Great movie to wind down the day before bed on some days too. Calming compared to most kids mobies, And cute!

My daughter has been trying to get this dvd since she checked it out at the library. I was extremely pleased to see it available and at such a great buy!! I was able to make my daughter's year without hurting my pockets!
